-- Electric car maker Miles Electric Vehicles files for bankruptcy
-- 
-- Tue Jun 11, 2013 1:57am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/11/us-mileselectric-bankruptcy-idUSBRE95A06K20130611

 

 (Reuters) - U.S. electric car manufacturer Miles Electric Vehicles filed for chapter 11 bankruptcy early on Tuesday, court documents showed. 
 The company listed estimated assets in the range of $10 million to $50 million, and estimated liabilities of between $50 million and $100 million. The case is in re Miles Electric Vehicles, Case No. 13-11511, U.S. Bankruptcy Court, District of Delaware. (Reporting by  Sakthi Prasad  in Bangalore; editing by  Patrick Graham )